aboutTitle: My passion is building cool stuff.
aboutContent: I started my learning journey at the Academy of Digital Industries , where I studied JavaScript and React. After completing my initial studies, I continued learning on my own. Once I became confident in React and related technologies, I moved on to backend development, focusing on PHP, Laravel, and CodeIgniter. I taught myself these technologies entirely and believe I have achieved a strong proficiency in them. Additionally, I am skilled in MySQL
